---
import "../styles/privacy-policy.css";
import BaseLayout from "../layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import privacyHero from "../assets/privacy-policy.svg"; // Optional visual aid
---
<BaseLayout title="Heliox – Privacy Policy">
  <main class="privacy-container">
    <section class="header-section">
      <a class="back-button" href="/signup">← Back to Signup</a>
      <div class="header-text">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Heliox. Your privacy and trust are essential to us. We created this page to be transparent, clear, and honest — just like our app.</p>
      </div>
      <img src={privacyHero.src} alt="Privacy visual" class="privacy-image" width="120" height="120" />
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>🔍 What is Heliox?</h2>
      <p>Heliox is a mindful daily challenge companion designed to help you track, reflect, and grow. Unlike task managers, we don’t overload you with to-dos. Instead, we give you space to build consistency, mental clarity, and small wins each day.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>🛡️ What Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We only collect the information absolutely necessary to provide our services. Here's what we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Details</strong>: Your name, email, and password (encrypted).</li>
        <li><strong>Challenge Logs</strong>: Your entries for each day. These stay private and are only visible to you.</li>
        <li><strong>Device Info</strong>: Minimal information used only for analytics and bug tracking.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>🔐 How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>Everything we collect is used to help you build better habits and get the most out of Heliox. That includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Letting you sign in securely</li>
        <li>Saving and syncing your daily logs</li>
        <li>Improving our user experience and fixing issues</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>🤝 We Do Not Sell Your Data</h2>
      <p>We respect your time and your trust. Your data is never shared with third-party marketers or advertisers. Any third-party services (like hosting or email delivery) only have access to the minimum needed to function — and only under strict confidentiality.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>📦 Data Ownership</h2>
      <p>Your logs are yours. You can request to download or delete your data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:support@heliox.app">support@heliox.app</a>. No complicated process. Just ask, and we’ll do it quickly.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>📆 Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>If we ever change how your data is handled, we will notify you in the app and via email. Transparency is key to building trust.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section contact-box">
      <h2>📬 Questions?</h2>
      <p>We’re real people who care. Reach out anytime with privacy concerns at <a href="mailto:support@heliox.app">support@heliox.app</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>